    # ├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм 10. Error / Stack Trace Information Leakage ├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм├втАЭтВм\par 
    def _check_error_leakage(self):\par 
        error_urls = [\par 
            f"\{self.target\}/error_test",\par 
            f"\{self.target\}/nonexistent_path_xyz",\par 
            f"\{self.target\}/search?q=" + "' AND 1=CONVERT(int,'error')--",\par 
        ]\par 
        leak_patterns = [\par 
            (r"traceback",       "Python traceback exposed"),\par 
            (r"werkzeug",        "Werkzeug/Flask debug info exposed"),\par 
            (r"ZeroDivisionError", "Python exception class name visible"),\par 
            (r"Internal Server Error.*File.*line \\d+",\par 
             "Stack frame with file/line info exposed"),\par 
            (r"query was:",      "Raw SQL query exposed in error message"),\par 
            (r"syntax error",    "Database error message exposed"),\par 
        ]\par 
        for url in error_urls:\par 
            try:\par 
                resp = self.session.get(url, timeout=self.timeout)\par 
                if resp.status_code in (500, 400, 200):\par 
                    for pattern, desc in leak_patterns:\par 
                        if re.search(pattern, resp.text, re.IGNORECASE):\par 
                            self._add(\par 
                                vuln_type  = "Error / Stack Trace Information Leakage",\par 
                                detail     = f"\{desc\} at \{url\}",\par 
                                severity   = "HIGH",\par 
                                cwe        = "CWE-209",\par 
                                mitre      = "T1592",\par 
                                evidence   = (\par 
                                    f"GET \{url\} ├втАатАЩ HTTP \{resp.status_code\} | "\par 
                                    f"Pattern '\{pattern\}' matched in live response"\par 
                                ),\par 
                                check      = "_check_error_leakage",\par 
                                confirmed  = True,\par 
                                recommendation = (\par 
                                    "Disable debug mode and custom error handlers. "\par 
                                    "Return generic 500 pages in production. "\par 
                                    "Never expose stack traces to end users."\par 
                                ),\par 
                            )\par 
                            break\par 
            except Exception:\par 
                continue\par 
